2
00:01:26.336 --> 00:01:28.297
<b>Dr. Randa?</b>

3
00:01:28.380 --> 00:01:30.424
<b>They're ready for you.</b>

4
00:02:16.220 --> 00:02:17.971
<b>Hiroshi…</b>

5
00:02:18.055 --> 00:02:21.475
<b>meet your son.</b>

6
00:02:23.894 --> 00:02:26.813
<b>Not the way you wanted it to be…</b>

7
00:02:26.897 --> 00:02:28.440
<b>I know…</b>

8
00:02:28.524 --> 00:02:30.234
<b>I never said that…</b>

9
00:02:30.317 --> 00:02:31.985
<b>It's just…</b>

10
00:02:32.069 --> 00:02:36.698
<b>I thought the two of us
were all we needed.</b>

11
00:02:39.952 --> 00:02:45.040
<b>I thought of taking your father's name…</b>

12
00:02:45.123 --> 00:02:47.125
<b>William.</b>

13
00:02:49.628 --> 00:02:52.548
<b>We can call him Bill.</b>

14
00:02:53.215 --> 00:02:56.593
<b>That was my stepfather's name.</b>

15
00:02:56.677 --> 00:02:58.846
<b>My father's name was…</b>

16
00:02:58.929 --> 00:03:00.556
<b>Kentaro.</b>

17
00:03:35.465 --> 00:03:37.551
<b>It's okay. Kentaro.</b>

18
00:03:37.634 --> 00:03:40.012
<b>I'm here.</b>

19
00:05:24.324 --> 00:05:25.325
<b>Wait.</b>

20
00:05:26.034 --> 00:05:27.035
<b>Wait.</b>

21
00:05:38.130 --> 00:05:40.007
<b>Please. I need to talk to you.</b>

22
00:05:40.757 --> 00:05:42.926
<b>We don't have time.</b>

23
00:05:43.010 --> 00:05:45.345
<b>If the Titan is heading to Santa Soledad.</b>

24
00:05:45.429 --> 00:05:48.599
<b>we need to get there and find a way to
send it back where it came from.</b>

25
00:05:48.682 --> 00:05:50.684
<b>Please. Let me see that letter.</b>

26
00:05:51.977 --> 00:05:53.187
<b>Of course.</b>

27
00:05:53.645 --> 00:05:55.105
<b>Forgive me for reading it.</b>

28
00:05:55.189 --> 00:05:57.566
<b>It belongs to you…</b>

29
00:05:57.649 --> 00:05:58.775
<b>…and Uncle Lee.</b>

30
00:05:58.859 --> 00:05:59.860
<b>I need to explain.</b>

31
00:05:59.943 --> 00:06:02.404
<b>You don't owe me an explanation.</b>

32
00:06:02.487 --> 00:06:04.156
<b>Your business is your own.</b>

33
00:06:04.239 --> 00:06:06.950
<b>It was just a one-time mistake.</b>

34
00:06:14.958 --> 00:06:16.335
<b>Really?</b>

35
00:06:17.711 --> 00:06:20.255
<b>That letter doesn't seem like a "mistake."</b>

36
00:39:38.712 --> 00:39:40.839
<b>Remember our song?</b>

37
